<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4557] Do something better than UnknownScannerException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4557</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;UnknownScannerException is a plague, there&apos;s no reason we should not at least try to create a new scanner. If that fails again, maybe try automatically setting a lower scanner caching (if possible and with proper loggin) and retry again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
